{"tid":2241394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武肺癱瘓海上旅業  土船塢成郵輪墳場","createTime":"2020-10-13T09:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T10:06:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"21bc68f5a0809f06b2a94321f8ea25a1190de445","tid":2241394,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201012/PU32GTMWAVCGZB65CRA7D3G5CU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201012%2FPU32GTMWAVCGZB65CRA7D3G5CU%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=ec9b5d08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201012%2FPU32GTMWAVCGZB65CRA7D3G5CU%2F&h=115773d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201012/PU32GTMWAVCGZB65CRA7D3G5CU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n武肺癱瘓海上旅業 <br />\n土船塢成郵輪墳場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Xr3INQTfVE7BAPUArDu30M46_Eg=/2661x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UQS76CUWOJCFFMM2KSQYN3CWAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXr3INQTfVE7BAPUArDu30M46_Eg%3D%2F2661x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUQS76CUWOJCFFMM2KSQYN3CWAI.jpg&h=9d05dc58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■土耳其的阿利亞加船塢擠滿在武肺疫情中提前退役的郵輪，如像郵輪墳場。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情下郵輪業癱瘓，土耳其愛琴海岸的阿利亞加（Aliaga）船塢成為郵輪墳場，擠滿五艘高至少10層、身長約260米的退役郵輪，有待拆件出售。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：全球疫情回升 中南美洲確診破千萬<br />\n<br />\n該五艘船分別屬於兩間郵輪公司，其中一間是專營巴哈馬和墨西哥的太平洋海岸航線的嘉年華公司，其中一艘被回收的郵輪是1988年投入服務的「海霸王號」（Sovereign of the Seas），由前美國總統卡特的夫人羅莎琳命名，可載逾2,700名乘客。另一艘是「嘉年華靈感號」（Carnival Inspiration），內設搖滾舞廳、圖書館和撲克牌賭廳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拆件規模空前<br />\n<br />\n船隻回收業協會主席奧納爾（Kamil Onal）指，之後會再有兩艘英國郵輪到此停泊等待被回收，由於把郵輪拆件是費時的巨型工序，一艘郵輪需時可長達一年，他指已額外增聘1,000名員工拆件，「今日的情況前所未見。過去10年，我們合共只回收了四至五艘郵輪，而且體積都比眼前這些小。今年回收的至少多達七艘。」<br />\n<br />\n這些郵輪過去數十年曾載不少英國人出海度假。威爾斯一名曾任職老師的女士憶述17年首次乘坐「嘉年華靈感號」出海，至今仍忘不了當年首次踏上甲板的震撼，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英損688億元<br />\n<br />\n自疫情在今年3月發酵後，英國以至全球的郵輪公司均自願停運。國際郵輪協會統計全球有近120萬名從業員生計受影響。協會副主席格林（Julie Green）說：「這段日子對於郵輪公司和整個供應鏈都十分艱巨。」她指郵輪業過去每年會為英國經濟帶來100億英鎊（1,011億港元）的經濟貢獻，支援逾8.8萬個職位，遍及旅遊業和餐飲業。她估計自封鎖措施落實後，郵輪業停運對英國經濟損失約68億英鎊（688億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府至今仍建議國民避免乘郵輪出海，而歐洲有郵輪公司已重啟營運，加強防疫措施，並強制所有乘客和船員接受檢測，以免重蹈疫輪「鑽石公主號」的覆轍。格林說：。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《星期日泰晤士報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sMMWWVi7QTx-M6K2GbGIwHOwXF0=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S4DI5U5THVHILMQ3RESQGN4RT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsMMWWVi7QTx-M6K2GbGIwHOwXF0%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS4DI5U5THVHILMQ3RESQGN4RT4.jpg&h=36d26457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■五艘退役郵輪已局部拆毀，露出超過十層船艙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mBXSZfOscwXk-BP4JrXFxC2dgeY=/1318x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/US6S7TEVONBDTEVO7EYS7Q46RY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmBXSZfOscwXk-BP4JrXFxC2dgeY%3D%2F1318x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUS6S7TEVONBDTEVO7EYS7Q46RY.jpg&h=66b97bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■郵輪拆下的鋼材將當廢鐵轉售，一些仍有用的物資則會成「夜冷貨」。"},{"pid":"79cb8d90b55992c0b18f1698b9c056cbb3e82810","tid":2241394,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:27:40.000Z","msg":"唔打死支共，以後陸續有嚟，班左膠繼續奶共啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8a3cd835a877baba1c2ee44a3e077b42fcfb32","tid":2241394,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:35:17.000Z","msg":"D救艇會唔會有人再用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e470e0e422cb505a4a32596e04e564f3ad3925","tid":2241394,"uid":27482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:38:01.000Z","msg":"做鬼屋應該有得諗"},{"pid":"73ea51b25e9c1b25472ac24b6365a0934d0b1a31","tid":2241394,"uid":180634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"泊係香港當屋住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64227bdc1a2c2977538e2c46d4b36cef43470e94","tid":2241394,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:04:44.000Z","msg":"d 飛機又泊晒係邊<br />\n大多數機場都收泊位費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a75a0aa76974edb68cb2574af69dde059596b4","tid":2241394,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287d7f1164519a986f7a8c9093783f0178c95556","tid":2241394,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64227bdc1a2c2977538e2c46d4b36cef43470e94","tid":2241394,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:04:44.000Z","msg":"d 飛機又泊晒係邊<br />\n大多數機場都收泊位費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:06:20.000Z","msg":"澳洲沙漠"}]}